item.title: Wrapping-up Petra
item.description: In only a few hours I am to get on a plane and begin the next phase of my adventures this summer. The last six weeks have blown by much faster than I can believe. But, c’est la vie I suppose. I don’t really have much to say at this point, though maybe it’s just because I’m so tired. We spent the day driving to Amman and relaxing in our hotel rooms, but though my body is exhausted, my mind is too excited to sleep.
